Series VII: Academic and Biographical Materials

Terence Sellers was an author and researcher specializing in experimental psychology and psychodrama. The website contains her CV, portraits, summaries of her writings, a blog containg chapters of her novel "One Decadent Life," and other writings by Sellers and her father J. Robert Sellers.
Robots.txt (a piece of code designed to limit crawler activity within a website) was ignored.

Certain file types will not be captured dependent on how they are embedded in the site. Other parts of websites that the crawler has difficulty capturing includes Javascript, streaming content, database-driven content, and highly interactive content.
